######################################################################
# README # naveen (naveenium.com) - 20090528
######################################################################

I just started developing for Adobe AIR like 15 minutes ago, so
bear with me here. :)

I wanted a small desktop app that I could run in the corner that
would auto-refresh and show me where my friends currently are. So
I whipped up this app quick. It basically wraps the foursquare
mobile web (http://m.playfoursquare.com) and refreshes once every
5 minutes.

In the future:
 - attach this to the foursquare API
 - make it slick.

